                        .5% for 3 sec</td
                    >
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div slot="box-right">
        <h3>URA Build</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Goal stats:</b> - # speed, # stam, # power, # guts, # wit
