            </li>
            <li>
                Gourman will either turn into starved monster or glutton of
                kasamatsu, prioritize based on stam/speed balance
            </li>
            <li>
                You'll want to get 15000 fans to unlock monsterous cornering
                (random corner increase accelerationby 40% and recoery stamin by
                1.5% for 3 sec) you will also have to win both the Mile Champ
                and Yasuda Kinen OR a short
            </li>
        </ul>
        <h4>junior year</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Prioritize rainbow training as always</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Classics</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>
